{
  "stem": "24259.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I-- on many occasions, my parents would mention that to us after we were liberated, that we were quite fortunate that, at that point in time, we were not discovered because of that.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This second farmer, again, kept us for approximately maybe eight or nine months, again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this time, he became very nervous about-- because he would hear that other farmers were caught hiding Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, they would be killed, along with the Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he became quite nervous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as a result, he made us leave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, again, my father persuaded him to keep us a couple extra days while he, again, went out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, again, every time my father would go out would be during the night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, again, he went out contacting other acquaintances, other farmers in the area, that he had confidence in their friendship.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, again, he persuaded another farmer to hide us in a similar fashion as the first two.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so my father came back and took us and brought us to the third farmer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably in the fall.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It seems every time we had to move around, it-- it was getting cold, and it was cold and so forth.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, again, my father would kind of persuade the farmer-- that was part-- part of the persuasion process-- that it was very cold.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and he would have pity on us, so to speak, and take us in because of that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I think that brings us into 1944 and so on, during the last, the third farmer, we were liberated kind of the end of '44, beginning of '45, during that winter.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His last name was Obanuk, O-B-A-N-U-K.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again, the spelling might not be exactly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this is the way, again, the name sounds.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
